lead_paragraph: Paraguay's Carlos Franco rallied to win the Shaw Charity Classic on Sunday at chilly Canyon Meadows for his first PGA Tour Champions victory.

headline.print_headline: Paraguay's Carlos Franco Wins Shaw Charity Classic
